Customer: Haan ji sir, hello.
Executive: Haan ji.
Customer: Haan ji sir.
Customer: Haan ji madam, maine ye India Mart se apni company jo listing ki thi kai din do teen din ho chuke hain.
Executive: Flexi Mold Enterprises.
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Haan sir, main hi baat kar rahi hoon Muskan abhi aap se baat ho rahi thi na.
Customer: Achcha achcha.
Executive: Sir aapko trust nahi aa raha tha na isiliye aapne is number pe call kiya koi nahi sir. Acchi baat hai aapne verify kiya. Aap waha se bhi call kar sakte ho but maine aapko jo official number se call kiya tha waha pe bhi connect kar sakte ho whatsapp pe bhi maine isiliye hi drop kar diya hai. In case wo number nahi contact mein hota hai to aap is number pe mujhe directly reach out kar sakte ho aapne abhi contact detail mein dekh liya hoga ki mera naam waha pe aa raha hoga right Muskan Choudhary.
Hmm hmm.
Executive: Theek hai aur ye mera yaha se bhi aap call kar sakte ho but most probably aap direct us number pe karoge to waha se mera reach out jyada hoga kyuki wo hamara official number hai ye aapka landline number hota hai.
Customer: Haan theek hai ji.
Executive: Ji sir to as of now isiliye maine aapko connect kiya tha kyuki aapki ye jo profile hai na isse mujhe update karna tha aapke keywords se related.
Hmm hmm.
Executive: To aap mujhe apna mail id bataoge sir?
Customer: Mail id madam Flexi Mold. Ek minute sir.
Executive: Haan ji sir bataye Flexi.
Customer: Mold Enterprise@gmail.com.
Executive: Enterprises to nahi hai sir?
Customer: Nahi price hai menu.
Executive: @gmail.com right?
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Flexi Mold Enterprise@gmail.com. Sir check kariye aapke pass mail aaya hoga.
Customer: Dekhta hu. India Mart ke name se aap call pe hi rahiye uske baad dekhiye sir.
Executive: Abhi deliver hua hoga.
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Aap usme na open kariye us mail ko.
Customer: Hmm.
Customer: Kar liya ji.
Executive: Open kiya aapne?
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Waha pe aaya hoga join with Google Meet.
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Uspe click karo aap.
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Aur join kariye.

- Customer wants to verify the executive's identity.

- Wants to update profile with keywords.

- Executive sent a Google Meet link to customer's email.

None
